import React from 'react' import { Table } from '../TableUser' export default function MyOrderRejectedList({myRejectedOrderData}) { return ( <> Service Price Provider Provider's Email Provider's Phone {myRejectedOrderData.length>0 && myRejectedOrderData.map((rejected)=>( <> {rejected.services.title} {rejected.services.price} {rejected.services.user.name} {rejected.services.user.email} {rejected.services.user.phone} ))}
) }
